PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?artMovement ?artMovementLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q5593 wdt:P135 ?artMovement .
  ?artMovement rdfs:label ?artMovementLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?artMovementLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?postalCode WHERE {
  ?place wdt:P281 ?postalCode .
  ?place wdt:P131 wd:Q5083 .
  FILTER ( REGEX( ?postalCode , "^[0-9]{5}(-[0-9]{4})?$" ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?boyfriend ?boyfriendLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q575689 wdt:P451 ?boyfriend .
  ?boyfriend rdfs:label ?boyfriendLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?boyfriendLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?senator ?senatorLabel WHERE {
  ?senator p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q4416090 ; pq:P768 ?seat ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
  ?seat wdt:P131 wd:Q1370 .
  FILTER ( ?start < "2014-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?senatorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?invention ?inventionLabel WHERE {
  ?invention wdt:P61 wd:Q762 .
  ?invention wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q14208553 .
  ?invention rdfs:label ?inventionLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?inventionLabel ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?coach ?coachLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2013-12-31T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?coach rdfs:label ?coachLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?coachLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?vicePresident ?vicePresidentLabel WHERE {
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?vpPosition .
  ?vpPosition ps:P39 wd:Q11699 ; pq:P580 ?vpStartTime .
  wd:Q1124 p:P39 ?presPosition .
  ?presPosition ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?presStartTime .
  FILTER ( ?vpStartTime = ?presStartTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?vicePresident rdfs:label ?vicePresidentLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?vicePresidentLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q23831 p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor ; pq:P453 wd:Q4169030 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?teamLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q221048 wdt:P54 ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?draftDate WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P647 ?stmt .
  ?stmt pq:P793 wd:Q972098 .
  wd:Q972098 wdt:P585 ?draftDate .
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?date WHERE {
  ?event wdt:P31 wd:Q211872 .
  ?event wdt:P1346 wd:Q203008 .
  ?event wdt:P585 ?date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q33866 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?startDate .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?governor ?governorLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  ?governor p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q17989863 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2011-12-31T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "2011-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?governor rdfs:label ?governorLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?governorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?start
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?year WHERE {
  ?event wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q32096 ; wdt:P1923 wd:Q221878 ; wdt:P585 ?date .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel ?start WHERE {
  ?person p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q844587 ; pq:P580 ?start .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  }
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2011-12-31T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ( ! BOUND( ?end ) || ?end >= "2011-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) ) ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?personLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?start

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?language ?languageLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q889 wdt:P37 ?language .
  FILTER ( ?language IN ( wd:Q178440 , wd:Q58680 ) ) ?language rdfs:label ?languageLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?languageLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q91 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
}
